        "detailedDescription_md": "Labor Department of Chhattisgarh State started this scheme &amp;amp;quot;Safai Karmakaar Ke Putr/Putri Hetu Vishesh Coaching Yojana&amp;amp;quot; for unorganized worker on 11 March 2015. The main objective of the scheme to provide financial assistance for free coaching. \n",
        "benefits_md": "> The fee for special coaching for admission in engineering, medical, CA and MBA or other professional education to the son/daughter (two children) studying in class 10th and above will be paid by the board.\n\n",
